title: Kutler - Abuse of Power - The New Nixon Tapes 1997
description:
ABUSE OF POWER - THE NEW NIXON TAPES 1997
Edited with introduction and commentary by Stanley I. Kutler
Released by Free Press in 1997

Dove Audio, 6 cassettes
12 MP3 files, 128 kbps 44 khz, monophonic

Dramatic readings of selected transcripts of the White House recordings made by President Richard M. Nixon between 1971 and 1973.  There is lots of commentary between readings to provide historical context and interpretation.
